snippet.textDisplay:
I love how progressive Indian music is becoming. For lovers of both Indian classical and western prog rock, this is a real treat. 
Great job guys and I hope to keep hearing a lot more this kind of stuff! 

Special mention to Hitesh, Sukhwinder, Gino and the flautist :D
